  <dinner><![CDATA[<p>3 course evening meal with a choice of starter, main course and dessert, (choice of main course and dessert for children aged 2-11yrs). Meals are served 6 evenings a week, not Tuesdays as the restaurant is closed. 1 lunch is included and served on Fridays which can be taken as a picnic.</p>]]></dinner>
